    "stability": "conditional",
    "condition_number_kappa": 700,
    "condition_number_effective": 10,
    "regime": "Well-posed with multi-frequency unwrap (3 f_mod sufficient for Chinese Remainder Theorem unwrap). Precision sigma_d ~ c / (4*pi*f_mod * sqrt(SNR)). Multipath interference (MPI) at concave corners and translucent surfaces biases depth; motion during 4-bucket integration causes phase artifacts."
